WEBVTT

00:05:25.932 --> 00:05:30.806
kwa kutafakari kila siku, kufanya yoga na kula vizuri kiasi.

00:05:30.830 --> 00:05:31.898
(Kicheko)

00:05:31.922 --> 00:05:34.144
Kama nikiona kwamba hali inaanza kuwa mbaya,

00:05:34.168 --> 00:05:36.212
Huwa nawasiliana na mtoa tiba wangu,

00:05:36.236 --> 00:05:39.299
mwanamke mweusi anayeitwa Dawn Armstrong,

00:05:39.323 --> 00:05:41.296
ambaye ni mcheshi

00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:43.557
na mwenye uzoea ambao hunipa faraja.

00:05:45.126 --> 00:05:46.764
Daima nitajuta

00:05:47.390 --> 00:05:49.456
sikuwepo kumsaidia mpwa wangu.

00:05:50.226 --> 00:05:52.013
Lakini tumaini langu la kweli

00:05:52.695 --> 00:05:55.766
ni kwamba niwahamasishe wengine kutokana na somo nililojifunza.

00:05:59.182 --> 00:06:01.652
Maisha ni mazuri.